17:39.630 --> 17:40.110
Kalau begitu,

17:40.110 --> 17:41.230
dia dibawa pergi

17:41.230 --> 17:41.830
dalam perjalanan pulang.

17:42.150 --> 17:42.440
Benar.

17:42.910 --> 17:43.670
Ponsel Wang Qianqian

17:43.790 --> 17:44.550
